        <p style="color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">
         Obviously, given the performance, understanding how RenTech does it has been a fascination of finance types for a long time. In 2019, Gregory Zuckerman published an excellent book,
         <em>
          <a href="https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkEtvhCAQgH-NHA0vVzxwaLPZ46ZJt2fDY1SyCgax1v764npoQoYMMPMNn1EJ-hB3OYcloSO0aZ9BetiWEVKCiNYFYuusJBcqWMUbZCW3RFQCuaXtIsCk3ChTXAHNqx6dUckF_6rAmFZokJ2yHeaai9oAJjVQig1uRGWxJboxcHLVah14AxK-Ie7BAxrlkNK8FOytoLe8tm0r1aR-gy9NmPKBnXN4x_UHud8fn9fjFbu1uUmwzvcFu349bqKgF52eMWcEOUlxpjMqCK0YbUpaWsU6YjpGlGaGGVP-DBvTaiUFx1NPy2XVS1LmeSBRlD4kHeLRnePnoCYYXxf5523ep9W7tOcJlB7BnlLS6falqe3BQ8zObatSNsoFr_NEgpLqlJCtVYRwQihGmWxDrvL_0D9IkY9R" rel="" style="color: #1a1a1a; text-decoration: underline;">
           The Man Who Solved the Market: How Jim Simons Launched the Quant Revolution
          </a>
         </em>
         , that gives the most complete glimpse.
        </p>
